# Coverage configuration.
#
# Seed / synthetic-data generators are operational scripts, not application
# logic — they build demo datasets and are never unit-tested (testing a data
# generator chases coverage rather than correctness). They are omitted so the
# coverage gate measures the real app-code denominator. The pattern is scoped
# narrowly to the seed modules only — it must NOT mask any real app code.
#
# (Phase 3 note: the new synthetic TCO generator still gets ONE invariant smoke
# test for correctness — that it runs and produces consistent cross-layer rows.)
[run]
omit =
    app/seed.py
    app/seed_demo.py
    app/seed_history.py
    app/seed_tracking.py
    app/seed_costing.py
    app/seed_tco.py
